Mu kipungo kya printemps mu kipwa kya 33 bipungo byetu ( B.B . ) , abayipayile Yesu a mu Nazarete .
Abamudimbiile’shi ntomboshi , abo nkumukupila bikile na kumupudika ku mutshi .
Anka Efile Mukulu baadi mumusangule ku bafwe , na kunyima kwa mafuku 40 , Yesu bakamiine mwiyilu .
Uno mwisambo wa kukaanya atwiupete mu ma Evanjile ananka a Bifundwe bya kiina Greke bya bwina Kidishitu byabakambaa kwitamina bu Kilombeeno kipya .
( 1 Beena - Kodinda 15 : 14 ) Ku lungi lupese , su ino myanda ibaadi ikitshikye binyibinyi , kwi lukulupilo lwibuwa bwa bantu loodi mulombeene namu kukulupila .
Byabya , myanda i mu ma Evanjile , ngya binyibinyi su ngya kupwandjikisha ?
Mu kwilekeena na myeele ya mpwandjikishi , myanda yabadi bafunde mu ma Evanjile ngya binyibinyi na mbeyitaluule kalolo .
Bu kileshesho , mwi mashina a ma mbalo a binyibinyi , ebungi a ku aa ma mbalo e kwanka na lelo uno .
Abemwisambila bantu ba binyibinyi babadi bashinkamishe mpa na kwi bantu bashii beena Kidishitu . — Luuka 3 : 1 , 2 , 23 .
Yesu aye nabeene abamwisambila kwi bafundji bashii beena Kidishitu ba mu siekele a kumpala na a kabidi .
* Mushindo ubaabadi bamwipee wabadi baleeshe mu ma Evanjile ngwipusheene na bibaabadi abayipaa bantu mu mafuku a beena Looma .
Na dingi , myanda i mwanka mbeyilonde mushindo auleesha’shi ibaadi ikitshikye na ngya binyibinyi — abaleesha mpa na bilubilo bya bangi balongi ba Yesu .
( Mateo 26 : 56 ; Luuka 22 : 24 - 26 ; Yowano 18 : 10 , 11 ) Ino myanda yooso ayileesha’shi bafundji ba ma Evanjile abaadi balulame na abafundjile myanda ya binyibinyi pabitale Yesu .
Bu byabidi’shi Yesu baadi na muwa akupu aye nkufwa , bangi mbalombeene kwiyipusha pabitale lusangukilo lwaye .
Mpa na batumiibwa baaye tababaadi bakumiine pa babapushiishe’shi basanguka ku bafwe nya .
( Luuka 24 : 11 ) Babalekyele kwela mpaka pababamwene Yesu mupwe kusanguka bebatuukila pababaadi bebungye pa bupenka .
Mu ungi musango , baadi mutuukile bantu bakile pa 500 abaadi bamumone . — 1 Beena - Kodinda 15 : 6 .
Balongi ba Yesu abaadi balungule bantu booso na katshintshi bwa lusangukilo lwaye kushi kutshina kukwatshibwa na kwipayibwa — mpa na kwi bantu abaadi bamwipee .
( Bikitshino 4 : 1 - 3 , 10 , 19 , 20 ; 5 : 27 - 32 ) Bano balongi booso bebungi babaadya kwikala na katshintshi su taabaadi bashinkamishe’shi Yesu baadi musangukye binyibinyi ku bafwe ?
Kushinkamisha kwa’shi Yesu baadi musangukye , nyi kukwete kunyingisha beena Kidishitu pa nsenga kubanga kala mpa na binobino .
Miisambo i mu ma Evanjile pabitale lufu na lusangukilo lwa Yesu ayitusha bishinkamiisho bya myanda yooso ibaadi ikitshikye .
Su bweyibadika kalolo , ayikushinkamiisha’shi lufu na lusangukilo lwa Yesu mmyanda ya binyibinyi ibaadi ikitshikye .
We mulombeene kunyingisha lukumiino loobe nsaa yopusha bwakinyi ino myanda ibaadi ikitshikye .
Tacitus , mutandjikwe mu kipwa kya 55 B.B . , bafundjile’shi : “ Christus , kubafikile eshina dya [ beena Kidishitu ] , babamutshibiile kibawe kibukopo mu bufumu bwa Tiberius ku maboko kwa nsushi eetu Pontius Pilatus . ”
Yesu mbamwisambile dingi kwi Suetonius ( mu siekele a kumpala ) ; kwi ungi mufundji a myanda ya kala abetanyina bu Josephus ( mu siekele a kumpala ) ; na kwi Pliny ungi nfumu a mu Bithynie ( mu siekele a kumpala ) .
( 1 Mpyeele 1 : 24 , 25 ) Akupu , beshikwanyi na Yesu bebungi tababaadi balombeene kufunda myanda ilombeenene kukwasha bantu bwabadya kukumiina na kukulupila mwadi nya .
Mpyeele umune a ku batumiibwa ba Yesu bafundjile bino patibitale lusangukilo lwaye : “ Efile Mukulu baamusàngwishe mwifuku dyaakasatu , aye nkumupa bukome bwa kwileesha patooka , kushii kwi bantu ba - bisumanga , anka biinyibiinyi kwi tumonyi tubadiile kusangulwa kwi Efile Mukulu , atwe babaadiile naaye , na batome naaye kuunyima kwa kusanguka kwaye kwa ku bafwe . ”
Evanjile a Mateo etulungula’shi , nsaa ibaadi beena bipwilo ba sha mushikwa bapushe’shi Yesu basanguka , abakimbile bya kwimika mukandu wa lusangukilo lwaye kupela wapalakana . — Mateo 28 : 11 - 15 .
Bino abileesha’shi Yesu baadi akimbi bwa’shi lusangukilo lwaye lukutwe kuukibwa kwi baantu su ?
Nya , mwanda Mpyeele bafundjile bibaadi Yesu mwibalungule pabaakwile’shi : “ Kunyima , aye nkwitutumina eyi dya kuwukisha kwi bantu naa dya kutwala buno buukamonyi’shi : Aye ngi abadi basangule kwi Efile Mukulu bu nsushi aa abatala na bafwe . ”
Beena Kidishitu ba binyibinyi babakitshine bino na bakwete kuyididila na kwibikita . — Bikitshino 10 : 42 .
“ Milwisho ibatwelele pa nsenga pa mwanda wa muntu umune , Adame , yaya milwisho yafwisha lufu . ” — Beena - Looma 5 : 12 , EEM
We kwakula naminyi su bakwipusha’shi : “ Okumiina kwikala na muwa wa ikalaika ? ”
Bantu bebungi mbalombeene kwakula’shi abakumina kwikala nao , anka tabamono bu mwanda wa binyibinyi nya .
Abamba’shi lufu alukwataa muntu ooso , takwi mushindo wa kwilusuka nya .
Tubande kupwandjikisha su bashintuula lwalwa lunkonko bakwipusha’shi : “ Okumiina kufwa su ? ”
Pa kushii mwanda , bantu bebungi tabakumiinaa kufwa nya .
Bible aleesha’shi Efile Mukulu bapangile bantu na lukalo lwa kwikala na muwa .
Nyi bwakinyi Bible akula’shi : ‘ Mmupe eshimba dyetu kyuukilo kya bya ikalaika . ’ — Mulungudi 3 : 11 .
Anka bantu ta be na muwa wa ikalaika nya .
Efile Mukulu bakitshiine kintu kampanda bwa kulumbuula myanda su ?
Lwaluulo alutusha Bible alukumu kwishimba , mwanda alwituleesha bwakinyi Yesu bakyengyele na kufwa .
Shapitre isatu ya kumpala ya mukanda wa Kibangilo ayitulungula’shi Efile Mukulu bapangile Adame na Eeva na muwa ushi na nfudiilo , aye nkwibalungula kibaabadi na kya kukita bwabadya kwiulama .
Akupu , ayileesha bibabaadi bakutwe kukookyela Efile Mukulu na kushimisha wawa muwa .
Uno mwisambo wi mu ngakwilo mupelepele — bilombeene na bangi kupwandjikisha wanka bu mwele kushi bu mwanda wa binyibinyi .
Anka , mu mukanda wa Kibangilo na mu ma Evanjile mwi bishinkamisho byoso abileesha’shi ino myanda ibaadi ikitshikye .
Mbipeta kinyi bifwishe kukutwa kukookyela kwa Adame ?
Bible aluula’shi : “ Milwisho ibatwelele pa nsenga pa mwanda wa muntu umune , Adame , yaya milwisho yafwisha lufu . Byabya , lufu alukwata bantu boso mwanda boso mbalwishe . ”
Baadi mushimishe mpàngo ya kwikala na muwa wa ikalaika aye nkufwa .
Bu byatudi beekulu baaye , twi bapyane mulwisho .
Anka , Efile Mukulu bakitshiine kintu kampanda bwa kulumbuula myanda su ?
Efile Mukulu baatshile mpàngo bwa kukuula sunga kufuta kyakya kibaadi Adame mushimishe bwa bana baaye kyabetamina bu muwa wa ikalaika .
Mukanda wa Beena - Looma 6 : 23 awamba’shi : ‘ Efuto dya mulwisho ndufu . ’
Bino abileesha’shi masaku atuushe mulwisho nyi ndufu .
Mu mushindo umune , tukwete kulwisha na kupeta efuto aditukila ku mulwisho diikale lufu .
Twi batandjikwe mu mulwisho kushii mu kukumiina kwetu .
Nyi bwakinyi , na kifulo kyoso , Efile Mukulu batumine Mwan’aye Yesu bwadya kutwala ‘ efuto dya milwisho yetu . ’
Lufu lwa Yesu ndufungule eshinda aditwala ku muloo na ku muwa ushi na mpwilo
Bu bibaadi muntu umune mupwidikye Adame mukutwe kukookyela ako kwitufwishile mulwisho na lufu , bibaadi abitungu muntu mupwidikye akookyela mpa na ku lufu bwa kwitukatusha bwabwa bushito .
Bible apatuula bino p’aye kwakula’shi : “ Mwanda bu bibaadi kukutwa kukookyela kwa muntu umune nkufishe kibumbu kya bantu ku milwisho , byabya dimo , ku kukukookyela kwa muntu umune kibumbu kya bantu akitambula bululame . ”
Bakatukile mwiyilu , afika muntu mupwedikye * bwadya kwitufwila .
Pa mwanda wa byabya , twi na mushindo watudya kwikala balulame ku meeso kw’Efile Mukulu na kwikala na lukulupilo lwa muwa wa ikalaika .
Bwakinyi bibaadi na muulo bwa’shi Yesu afwe bwa kulombasha uno mwanda ?
Efile Mukulu sha bukome booso tabaadya penda kutadiila bana ba Adame bwabadya kwikala na muwa wa ikalaika ?
Su Efile Mukulu badya kutuula ku lupese kululama kwaye , bantu babadya kwiyipusha bibadya kwikala mululame mu myanda yooso .
Bu kileshesho , badya kuleesha kululama mu kusangula kwa bantu ba mu lutandwa lwa Adame balombane bwa kupeta muwa wa ikalaika ?
Tubadya kwikala atumukulupila bwa kulombasha milayilo yaaye su ?
Bu byaadi mushale mulamate ku kululama kwaye bwa kukimba kipandjilo kyetu , abitushinkamisha’shi Efile Mukulu ekala akitshi nka myanda ibuwa .
Ku bukwashi bwa mulambu wa lufu lwa Yesu , Efile Mukulu mmufungule eshinda aditwala ku muwa wa ikalaika mu Mpaladiiso pa nsenga .
Mayi a Yesu e mu mukanda wa Yowano 3 : 16 aamba’shi : “ Mwanda Efile Mukulu mmufule ba pano bikile , mu kipaso kyadi mupaane Mwan’aye eeleka , bwa’shi muntu ooso amukumiina taashiminanga , anka aikale na muwa wa ikalaika . ”
Lufu lwa Yesu talwi penda bwa kuleesha kululama kw’Efile Mukulu nya , anka aluleesha kifulo kyaye kikata bwa bantu .
Byabya , bwakinyi Yesu bakyengyele na kufwa lufu lwa makyenga lwabadi baleeshe mu ma Evanjile ?
P’aye kukookyela na kushala na lulamato , Yesu baadi muleeshe patooka madimi a Satana a kwamba’shi bantu ta mbalombeene kushala na lulamato kwi Efile Mukulu pabadi mu makyenga .
( Yoobo 2 : 4 , 5 ) Aa madimi abaadi amwenekye bu a binyibinyi kunyima kwa Satana kutwesha Adame mu mulwisho .
Anka , Yesu baadi mupwidikye bu bibaadi Adame — baadi mukookyele Efile Mukulu sunga mu makyenga .
( 1 Beena - Kodinda 15 : 45 ) Baadi mushinkamishe’shi Adame namu baadi na kya kukookyela Efile Mukulu su baadya kusangula bwa kwibikita .
P’aye kunyingiila mu mpombo , Yesu mmulekye kileshesho kya kulonda .
( 1 Mpyeele 2 : 21 ) Efile Mukulu baadi mufute Mwan’aye bwa kukookyela kwaye pa kumupa muwa ushii bya kufwa mwiyilu .
Yesu balesheshe kyatudi balombeene kukita p’aye kwakula’shi : “ Muwa wa looso namu ngi’shi bantu bakuukye , obe bupenka Efile a binyibinyi na yawa obotumine , Yesu Kidishitu . ” — Yowano 17 : 3 .
Bafundji ba uno jurnale abakutekye bwa kulonga ingi myanda pabitale Yehowa , Efile Mukulu a binyibinyi na pabitale Mwan’aye Yesu Kidishitu .
